Instructions

Inside the bin folder you will find an app
Inside the data folder in the bin you will find a file called mysettings.xml

Enter the desired video width and height for capture here (before you start the app).

Launch the app and press 's' for the settingsd (this allows you to select inputs and format)

When you are sett press 'd' (this will toggle the video draw) to turn off the video in the app- it will keep playing out syphon.